prompts.text: Create a close-up image of a highly detailed mech robot face, The mech's design should be sleek and futuristic, with visible hydraulic connections running along its neck and collar area. Instead of a human face, the head features a smooth, metallic surface with intricate panels and sensors. The robot's exterior is made of a combination of metal plating and exposed mechanical components, with gears and joints visible. The lighting should highlight the reflective surfaces and the complexity of the design, giving the mech a powerful and industrial feel.
